[normal]The City of London Corporation’s Role in Supporting Green Finance [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]What are the main drivers behind institutional investors’ decisions on the type of investments they include in their portfolios?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]How effective are the financial markets in matching available finance to the required investment in renewable energy and other green projects?[bold] [bold] [bold]To what extent is a potential “carbon bubble” a real risk?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]What should the Government be doing to help redirect finance to help fill the multi-billion [bold]pound [bold]green finance gap? How can ‘political risk’ to investors from changes to the Government’s energy and environmental policies be reduced? Can the Government ever remove political risk or are more innovative financial instruments that offset those risks the solution?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Is greater direction to banks needed to encourage them to increase their lending to renewable energy and green projects? [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]How can pension funds and other investors be encouraged to re-direct their capital funds towards investments with green objectives? [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Are fiscal incentives for people/institutions to put funds in green investments needed, and if so what?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]How can better information on the environmental impacts of investments and companies be provided to investors? What difference would such information make to investors in practice?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] What are the pros and cons of having a financial transaction tax (Tobin tax) with revenue hypothecated to support green investments? [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]What can the Government do to help increase the flow of finance to small and community-based renewable energy [bold]and green projects?[bold] [bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]What impact is the Green Investment Bank [bold](GIB) [bold]likely to have on the green finance gap? Does it have the right investment strategy[bold]?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
